Jide Macaulay (a mụrụ n'abalị  anọ n'ọnwa Nọvemba n'afọ 1966) bụ onye na-ahụ maka ikike LGBTQ nke Britain na Naijiria ma bụrụ onye ụkọchukwu site na Chọọchị Anglịkan nke England. Ọ bụ onye guzobere Pastọ nke ụlọ ofufe mbụ nke House Of Rainbow Nigeria maka ndị LGBTQ na Nigeria, a kwanyekwara ya ùgwù dị ka nwoke nke kachasị mma nke afọ 2007 bụ 2007 Man of the Year site na UK Black LGBT maka ọrụ ya n'inyere ndị LGBT nwere okwukwe aka.
